examples.en: It requires careful consideration.
The house requires painting.
We require our secretary to be on time.
You are required to obey.
The project will require a great amount of time and money.
She required that everyone attend / should attend the meeting.
Hard work will be required of students in this course.
Many jobs today require computer skills.
The toy requires four batteries, which are not included.
You are required by law to wear a seat belt.
The job will require a great deal of time and effort.
These issues require skillful handling.
This matter will require your undivided attention.
Most house plants require regular watering.
These items require careful handling.
He did not require a religion to be the column of society.
They store goods until consumers require them.
His labor did not require a great deal of skill.
Most professions in the medical field require years of training.
We require payment in advance for all goods purchased.
The sentence may seem to require another pointing.
The job will require a considerable input of money.
These plants require, before being planted out, to be stumped.
Desperate diseases call for / require desperate measures / remedies. .
Campbell's broken leg will probably require surgery.
What's required is a complete reorganization of the system.
Lengthier trips require more planning.
Dwellers require very careful handling.
The problem may require military action.
The rings require a strong upper body.
